<br>
Especially since the game could calculate a delta and update only the changes.<br>
<br>
This has been happening quite often of late, people in my guild have run up against it multiple times.  Loot something, and zone crashes, item gone.<br>
<br>
At the very least, the act of looting should force a hard save.<br>
<br>
<br>
Oh yes, I had a good chuckle out of the claim that zones crashing was &quot;not a bug&quot;.  I really wish their CS people were actually, say, honest, and just said &quot;As much as I would like to, I am forbidden by policy to reimburse for items lost after a zonecrash and rollback&quot;.  They'd look much less ignorant.<br>
